name: Darius FOXE, Petitioner v. Honorable Judge Sandy L.V. BIRD, President Judge, Phila. County, Respondent

parties: Darius FOXE, Petitioner v. Honorable Judge Sandy L.V. BIRD, President Judge, Phila. County, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM
AND NOW, this 13th day of October, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED, and the Prothonotary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM
